OL,3,CShould cruise ship passengers be
OL,4,Ccharged a tourist tax to visit
OL,5,CScotland?
OL,7,FAfter bringing in the Visitor Levy Act
OL,8,Flast year, which allows a tax to be
OL,9,Fcharged on certain overnight stays,
OL,10,Fsome have argued the principle should
OL,11,Fapply to those visiting by cruise ship.
OL,13,FA public consultation is now seeking
OL,14,Fviews on the benefits and problems a
OL,15,Fcruise ship levy could bring.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/18
