OL,3,CShould cruise ship passengers be
OL,4,Ccharged a tourist tax to visit
OL,5,CScotland?
OL,7,F"We can have a massive difference on
OL,8,Fspend and what they are spending on,
OL,9,Fdepending on the country they are
OL,10,Ffrom. An ideal cruise boat is when
OL,11,Fit's filled with American tourists and
OL,12,Fdocked just outside the restaurant."
OL,14,FMr Manson and other hospitality
OL,15,Fbusinesses have calculated that there
OL,16,Fare a maximum of 150 seats in the
OL,17,Ftown's restaurants or cafes at any one
OL,18,Ftime, so when some cruises carry 3,000
OL,19,Fpassengers, this can create a problem.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/18
