OL,3,CShould cruise ship passengers be
OL,4,Ccharged a tourist tax to visit
OL,5,CScotland?
OL,7,F"There's a lot of people that can
OL,8,Fleave a bit disappointed that they've
OL,9,Fnot managed to get a seat or a table
OL,10,Fin the restaurants or cafes," he added.
OL,12,FMr Manson believes a cruise ship tax
OL,13,Fcould be positive if the money was
OL,14,Fused to improve the local
OL,15,Finfrastructure around the island,
OL,16,Fincluding transport, public toilets
OL,17,Fand Wi-Fi, which are all under strain
OL,18,Fwhen a large cruise comes in.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/18
