OL,3,CShould cruise ship passengers be
OL,4,Ccharged a tourist tax to visit
OL,5,CScotland?
OL,7,FHe said: "I think it would maybe stop
OL,8,Fpeople coming off that didn't have an
OL,9,Finterest in seeing the place or
OL,10,Fexperiencing it. And definitely, I
OL,11,Fthink the money should be spent on
OL,12,Ffacilities that would improve the
OL,13,Flocal areas. There is no point in you
OL,14,Fpaying a cruise ship levy and then the
OL,15,Fmoney disappears into something that
OL,16,Fno one ever sees."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/18
