OL,3,CShould cruise ship passengers be
OL,4,Ccharged a tourist tax to visit
OL,5,CScotland?
OL,7,FLerwick has a population of around
OL,8,F7,000, so when a big cruise docks, it
OL,9,Fmeans that number rises by another
OL,10,F50%, which is why many local people
OL,11,Fdecide not to come into town on those
OL,12,Fdays as the streets, shops, cafes and
OL,13,Froads are too busy.
OL,15,FThe local council leader, Emma
OL,16,FMacdonald, says it is a difficult
OL,17,Fbalance between ensuring Shetland
OL,18,Fcontinues to be a popular tourist
OL,19,Fdestination and meeting the needs of
OL,20,Fthe local community.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/18
