OL,3,CShould cruise ship passengers be
OL,4,Ccharged a tourist tax to visit
OL,5,CScotland?
OL,7,F"It is really important that we do
OL,8,Fhave a good industry around cruise
OL,9,Fship visitors, but we've also got to
OL,10,Fkeep in mind that they can't have an
OL,11,Fimpact on the services that people
OL,12,Frely on day in and day out," she said.
OL,14,F"We don't want anything to happen that
OL,15,Fwill make people choose not to put
OL,16,FShetland on their itinerary, because
OL,17,Fthat's not good for the Port Authority
OL,18,Fand that's not good for the businesses
OL,19,Fwho rely on that tourism."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/18
