OL,3,CShould cruise ship passengers be
OL,4,Ccharged a tourist tax to visit
OL,5,CScotland?
OL,7,FThe local council is looking at all
OL,8,Foptions, including a point of entry
OL,9,Flevy, which would involve all visitors
OL,10,Fto Shetland paying one small fee, no
OL,11,Fmatter how they travel or how long
OL,12,Fthey stay.
OL,14,FMs Macdonald added: "I think it's not
OL,15,Flooking likely that it (the visitor
OL,16,Flevy) will make sense for us as a
OL,17,Fsmall local authority. We just don't
OL,18,Fget enough people to make the level of
OL,19,Fburden on our small businesses
OL,20,Fworthwhile.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/18
