OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F317A1747941398
OL,3,CShould cruise ship passengers be
OL,4,Ccharged a tourist tax to visit
OL,5,CScotland?
OL,7,F"It's thought that a point of entry
OL,8,Flevy that is maybe administered by
OL,9,FLoganair or North Link Ferries, might
OL,10,Fmake that kind of bureaucracy around
OL,11,Fit much easier. So we think that that
OL,12,Fis something that's worth looking at.
OL,13,FBut obviously, all these options are
OL,14,Fstill out there.
OL,16,F"We don't want people not to be able
OL,17,Fto afford to come here. Shetland is a
OL,18,Fbeautiful place to come. I think it's
OL,19,Fjust all about balance of making sure
OL,20,Fthat we fully understand what we're
OL,21,Fdoing."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/18
