OL,3,CShould cruise ship passengers be
OL,4,Ccharged a tourist tax to visit
OL,5,CScotland?
OL,7,FThe Director of Policy & External
OL,8,FAffairs at the British Ports
OL,9,FAssociation, Mark Simmonds, said: "It
OL,10,Fis alarming to see the Government
OL,11,Fpressing ahead with a consultation on
OL,12,Fplans that have no clear aims.
OL,14,F"Local levies in parts of Scotland
OL,15,Fwill alarm and confuse cruise industry
OL,16,Fplanners, who book visits years in
OL,17,Fadvance, and threaten growth and
OL,18,Finvestment across Scotland as vessels
OL,19,Ftend to call in multiple ports.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/18
