OL,3,CShould cruise ship passengers be
OL,4,Ccharged a tourist tax to visit
OL,5,CScotland?
OL,7,F"To raise any significant revenue, a
OL,8,Flevy would need to be set at a level
OL,9,Fthat would very likely deter cruise
OL,10,Fships calling in Scotland.
OL,12,F"The net result would be a loss to the
OL,13,FScottish economy with no real boost to
OL,14,Fcouncil coffers.
OL,16,F"The ports and cruise industries are
OL,17,Fboth open to engaging with national
OL,18,Fand local governments to solve
OL,19,Fspecific issues and always have been.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/18
