OL,7,F"A new tax on a successful and growing
OL,8,Findustry will simply make Scotland
OL,9,Fless attractive to calls in what is a
OL,10,Fhighly competitive and mobile market."
OL,12,FThe Scottish Government Finance
OL,13,FSecretary, Shona Robison, said: "The
OL,14,Ftourism sector is a crucially
OL,15,Fimportant part of the Scottish economy
OL,16,Fand cruise visits are increasing.
