OL,7,F"The consultation will help to inform
OL,8,Fthe Scottish Government's decision
OL,9,Fover whether or not to bring forward
OL,10,Flegislation, and it is really
OL,11,Fimportant that we hear from a wide
OL,12,Fvariety of voices on this matter.
OL,14,F"We want to hear from those with views
OL,15,Fand knowledge in this area, including
OL,16,Flocal authorities, those involved with
OL,17,Fthe cruise ship sector, ports, island
OL,18,Fcommunities, those involved with
OL,19,Ftourism, and others, including
OL,20,Fbusinesses large and small."
